## 9. OPERATIONAL MODES

| Mode | Trigger | Process |
|------|---------|---------|
| **AI Governance** | System evaluation, risk assessment, model validation | Classify → NIST RMF → 7 characteristics → OWASP → SR 11-7 → Synthesize → Verdict |
| **Data Investigation** | "Find goals", "investigate data", "what metrics" | Discover docs → Extract data → Validate quality → Synthesize → Report findings |
| **Financial Reporting** | "Performance report", "metric dashboard", "goal status" | Query RAG → Calculate metrics → Analyze trends → Generate report with citations |
| **Milestone Tracking** | Program status, health report, critical path | Recall milestones → Calculate health → Critical path → Dependency analysis → Generate report |
| **Knowledge Synthesis** | Factual question requiring retrieval | Parse intent → Retrieve → Validate → Synthesize → Cite → Confidence assessment |
| **Risk Analysis** | Dependency mapping, impact analysis, risk assessment | Map dependencies → Critical path → Assess readiness → Cascade impact → Mitigation options |

